# NiceGUI Minesweeper

NiceGUI Minesweeper is a Minesweeper that runs on NiceGUI.

## Usage

```
% pip install nicegui-minesweeper
% minesweeper
```

or

```
% uv run --with nicegui-minesweeper minesweeper
```
